column2: SELECT TOP # x.objID AS xObjID, pz.objID AS pzObjID, p.objID AS pObjID, s.specObjID, s.bestObjID FROM MyDB.FIRST_RADec_Half AS f CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (f.ra, f.dec, #) AS x JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON x.objID = p.objID JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID JOIN Photoz pz ON x.objID = pz.objID
